        "title": "[codex] Add iOS Apple Review demo mode",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- supersedes #90913 with a branch/title/body that reflect the Apple Review demo work\n- keeps the iOS App Store release prep on this branch, including iPhone-only submission metadata\n- adds an Apple Review offline demo mode activated by setup code `APPLE-REVIEW-DEMO`\n- accepts the demo setup code from QR scan, Settings, the legacy manual entry view, and the first-run Connect Gateway -> Set Up Manually flow\n- swaps Chat to a local demo transport in demo mode and disables Talk execution while no Gateway is available\n\n## App Review Flow\n\nApple reviewers can open the app, tap **Set Up Manually** on **Connect Gateway**, paste `APPLE-REVIEW-DEMO` in **Setup Code**, then tap **Apply Setup Code**. The app enters a local offline demo mode and does not require a running Gateway.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `git diff --check`\n- `pnpm ios:build`\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local` clean: no accepted/actionable findings\n- physical iPhone Debug build, install, and launch on `Nimrod’s iPhone` with bundle id `ai.openclaw.ios.test.guti-gzs353x62e`\n",
